# random in unclocked mode (no clock patched) draws a new value EVERY tick.
# steps default 0 -> continuous; minimum 0, maximum 1 -> output = randUniform().
# Seed 1 (golden default) gives a fixed sequence (values are the engine's float
# randUniform stream).
patch <<<
[random]
    output = O1
>>>
@0 expect O1 0.00006294 tol 1e-6
@1 expect O1 0.01574743 tol 1e-6
@2 expect O1 0.61640406 tol 1e-6
@3 expect O1 0.07161862 tol 1e-6
@4 expect O1 0.55848831 tol 1e-6
